Package: pkgspell
Type: Package
Title: Spell checker for R packages development
Version: 0.1.0.9001
Date: 2016-04-03
Authors@R: person("Iegor", "Rudnytskyi", email = "iegor.rudnytskyi@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool, which helps to automatically check all documentations'
    files of a developing package on typos and spelling errors.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://github.com/pkgspell
BugReports: https://github.com/irudnyts/pkgspell/issues
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
Imports:
    hunspell (>= 1.2)
    Rd2roxygen (>= 1.6)
Suggests:
    roxygen2 (>=4.1.1)
